condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA Schedule , Section II A | Description :Prep & furnish to Bank 2 impact assessment reports of implementationof RAP, first by May 31, 2009 second within 120 days of completion of all resettlement under the project | Due Date :31-May-2009
Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section I.1 | Description :GOI shall make Loan proceeds available to GOHP according to the agreedarrangements | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section II.B.2 | Description :RIDC shall prepare and furnish to the Bank quarterly ProjectReports including agreed performance monitoring indicators no later than 45 days after end of each quarter | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :LA Schedule 2, Section III | Description :All goods, works and services to be financed out of the Loan shall beprocured in accordance with the provisions of the Project Agreement | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule Section I.A | Description :GOHP shall maintain the Board of Directors of the RIDC with compositionand powers sufficient to direct the carrying out of the Project in a timely and effective manner. | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I.B | Description :GOHP shall maintain a dedicated team of suitably qualified staff in RIDCboth at HQ and in atleast 3 dedicated field divisions, with sufficient resources | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I.C | Description :RIDC shall prepare EMPs and RAP for Phase II roads in accordance withOperations Manual and R&R policy, satisfactory to the Bank | Due Date :05-Apr-2009
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I.D | Description :RIDC shall implement the Project in accordance with Operations Manual,EMPs, RAPs, Financial Management Manual | Frequency :Monthly
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I.E | Description :GOHP shall transfer Loan Proceeds to RIDC within 3 weeks of receivingthem from GOI | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I.F | Description :RIDC shall prepare and make public by March 31 of each year startingfrom 2008 an annual Road Maintenance Plan for core road network for following FY and implement it in a timely & efficient manner |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I.G | Description :RIDC shall prepare and make public by April 30 of each year startingfrom 2008 a core road network survey report and a maintenance achievement report for the proceeding FY | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II.B.2 | Description :RIDC shall maintain a financial management system in accordance withagreed requirements | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II.B.3 | Description :GOHP shall have the financial statements audited by acceptableauditors and furnish the Bank the audited reports no later than 6 months after the closing date for the statements | Frequency:Yearly
